  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Three seriously injured when a bus collided with a fuel queue",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Three persons were seriously injured when a private bus collided with a fuel queue at Urani in the Kokkuvil police area in Batticaloa and were admitted to the Batticaloa Teaching Hospital, Kokkuvil OIC Upul Prishad Wimalaratne said.",
        "The accident occurred when a private bus traveling towards Batticaloa collided with a group of people queuing for fuel in front of the Urani petrol station today (27).",
        "The injured are being treated and further investigations are being conducted by the Kokkuvil Police."
      ],
